| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-3267 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 2113b4b4-ca0a-53b3-8326-f739fcbdc598"
